data.description:
Indulge in the epitome of Montana living with this immaculate 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, ideally positioned near Canyon Ferry Lake and the state capital of Helena. The main level welcomes you with an open floor-plan kitchen, dining, and living room, creating a perfect space for entertaining. Two bedrooms (including master ensuite) and a versatile office/bonus room complete this level.

Descend to the lower level where a spacious family room awaits, accompanied by three additional bedrooms, a laundry room, and two bonus rooms that offer endless possibilities. Abundant storage throughout the home ensures that every inch is as practical as it is beautiful. The oversized double car garage and heated 3-seasons room contribute to the grandeur of this exceptional residence.

A short 25-30 minute drive brings you to Helena, where modern conveniences and an airport await. The area is a recreational paradise with multiple boat ramps within 5 miles on Canyon Ferry Lake and the Missouri River. Forest service access is just a mile down the gravel road, providing opportunities for hiking, hunting, UTV riding, and snowmobiling.

Outside, a well-established garden adorned with fruit trees and berry bushes awaits your green thumb. A deer fence surrounds the garden, preserving your hard work and deterring four-legged visitors. The main level deck offers stunning views of the Elkhorn mountains, creating the perfect backdrop for evening BBQs and sunset-watching.

Opportunities like this are rare – don't miss the chance to call this exceptional property home. Embrace the beauty of Montana living in this meticulously crafted haven where comfort, convenience, and natural splendor converge.
